                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5741" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1463</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8260 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“如烟”往事，“雾化”未来——中国电子烟企业的突围之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Disappearing past: &quot;Ru Yan&quot; e-cigarette, bright future:atomization technology——The development of China&#39;s e-cigarette firms</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐艳梅，王自强，宋夏，张亚楠，李想</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国科学院大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳易佳特科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子烟；外部环境；战略管理；组织合法性</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">E-cigarette; External environment; Strategic management; Organizational legitimacy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子烟作为一款源自中国，且在国际市场上占据绝对竞争优势的划时代创新产品，正在悄然但猛烈地改变着烟草行业，这对创新进程中的中国意义非凡。本案例通过韩力“如烟”的成败，展现宏观环境对行业及企业发展的影响；通过易佳特的技术创新展现企业在不同时期战略选择的变化，以及不同时期企业价值创造活动的差异性。以小见大，在刻画电子烟行业发展历程的同时，进一步引伸出商业生态变迁的动态性、综合性和复杂性等战略问题，明确企业核心能力的构建是一个经营策略变革和技术不断积累的过程。并且电子烟作为具有颠覆性创新性质的新兴行业，其出现、快速发展及未来走向，对许多同类型新兴行业及企业具有类比、借鉴作用，对国家产业政策的制定、丰富与完善具有推动作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The e-cigarette is an epoch-making innovation originated from China. It caused a revolution in the tobacco market quietly and violently. China&#39;s e-cigarette firms have an absolute competitive advantage in the market. This event is of great significance to China, which emphasizes innovation. This case demonstrates the impact of the macro environment on the development of the industry and the company through the success or failure of Han Li&#39;s &quot;Ruyan&quot;. Through the technological innovation of Aspire, it shows the differences in the strategic choices and value creation activities of firms in different periods, so as to reflect the application of value chain theory in reality. While portraying the development process of the e-cigarette industry, a series of strategic issues are further raised. It is clear that the construction of the core competence of a firm is a process of business strategy reform and continuous accumulation of technology. As an emerging industry with disruptive innovation nature, the emergence, rapid development and future direction of e-cigarettes have an analogy and reference role for similar firms, and promote the formulation and improvement of national industrial policies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
